---
import DriftAmbient from './DriftAmbient.astro';
---

<section class="hero">
  <DriftAmbient intensity={1} />
  <div class="hero__lamp" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="wrap hero__inner">
    <p class="eyebrow">An open-source game · in the making</p>

    <h1 class="hero__title">Elua</h1>

    <p class="hero__lede lede">
      Tessara is an immense, half-understood country, and not all of it runs
      smoothly. As one of its keepers, your work is to set it right again — to
      walk the round, read the land, mend what has drifted, and keep the lamp
      lit one more night. Your aunt is teaching you the craft, before her
      workshop becomes yours.
    </p>

    <div class="hero__cta">
      <a class="btn" href="#world">Step into the world</a>
      <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/open">Build it with us →</a>
    </div>

    <p class="hero__whisper muted">
      Tessara simply runs in four dimensions — and no one who lives there ever
      thinks to mention it.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="hero__fade" aria-hidden="true"></div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    isolation: isolate;
    min-height: min(92vh, 860px);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero__lamp {
    position: absolute;
    z-index: 0;
    top: -20%;
    left: 50%;
    width: 120vmax;
    height: 80vmax;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: radial-gradient(
      50% 50% at 50% 50%,
      rgba(227, 168, 87, 0.16),
      rgba(227, 168, 87, 0.05) 40%,
      transparent 65%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
    animation: lamp-breathe 11s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes lamp-breathe {
    0%,
    100% {
      opacity: 0.85;
      transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1);
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1.04);
    }
  }

  .hero__inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    padding-block: clamp(4rem, 12vh, 9rem);
    max-width: 50rem;
  }
  .hero__title {
    margin-top: 1.1rem;
    font-size: var(--step-5);
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    line-height: 0.95;
    background: linear-gradient(
      176deg,
      var(--ceramic-100) 30%,
      var(--lamp-300) 75%,
      var(--lamp-500)
    );
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 6px 40px rgba(227, 168, 87, 0.18));
  }
  .hero__lede {
    margin-top: 1.6rem;
    max-width: 38ch;
  }
  .hero__cta {
    margin-top: 2.2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.9rem;
  }
  .hero__whisper {
    margin-top: 2.6rem;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: var(--step-0);
    max-width: 42ch;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .hero__fade {
    position: absolute;
    inset-inline: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    height: 30%;
    z-index: 1;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, var(--night-900));
    pointer-events: none;
  }
</style>
